=head1 NAME

	CL_RFC1034_5_2_2_CNAME_match - CNAME RR matches the query type


=head1 VERIFICATION POINTS

	Verify that a NUT doesn't restarts the query when it encounters a CNAME

=begin html
	<UL>
	<li>The resolver should not pursue aliases when the CNAME RR matches the
query type</li>
	</ul> 

=end html

=head1 TARGET

	Client (with recursive function)

=head1 SYNOPSIS

=begin html
<PRE>
	<A HREF="./CL_RFC1034_5_2_2_CNAME_match.seq">CL_RFC1034_5_2_2_Encounter_CNAME.seq</A> [-tooloption ...]: KOI tool option
	See also <A HREF="../DNSConfig.pm">DNSConfig.pm</A>
</PRE>

=end html

